export declare const componentIndexContent = "# TNUI Component Index\n\nUse this file to narrow component choices before opening TNUI source code.\n\n## How To Use This File\n\n1. Pick the page intent: form, navigation, feedback, display, or layout\n2. Open the linked component doc\n3. Read the component doc before drilling into source\n4. Use `components/README.md` for coverage notes and source-only exceptions\n\nDetailed component docs live under `llm-docs/tnui/components/`.\n\n## Action And Trigger Components\n\n- [button](./components/button.md): primary trigger and action button\n- [action-sheet](./components/action-sheet.md): bottom action selection menu\n- [modal](./components/modal.md): confirm / alert modal flows with instance\n  control\n- [popup](./components/popup.md): general popup container for custom content\n- [notify](./components/notify.md): transient global feedback bar\n- [overlay](./components/overlay.md): bare mask layer with optional slot content\n- [bubble-box](./components/bubble-box.md): anchored micro-menu popover\n- [swipe-action](./components/swipe-action.md): gesture-revealed row actions\n\n## Form And Input Components\n\n- [form](./components/form.md): form container and field orchestration\n- [input](./components/input.md): text, textarea, password, and select-style\n  input\n- [checkbox](./components/checkbox.md): single checkbox and checkbox-group\n- [radio](./components/radio.md): single radio and radio-group selection\n- [switch](./components/switch.md): boolean or two-value immediate toggle\n- [picker](./components/picker.md): generic single, multi, and linkage picker\n- [date-time-picker](./components/date-time-picker.md): specialized date/time\n  popup picker\n- [region-picker](./components/region-picker.md): region hierarchy selector\n- [keyboard](./components/keyboard.md): custom numeric / ID / plate keyboard\n- [number-box](./components/number-box.md): numeric stepper input\n- [slider](./components/slider.md): single-value or range drag input\n- [rate](./components/rate.md): star or icon rating input\n- [image-upload](./components/image-upload.md): upload field for image lists\n- [search-box](./components/search-box.md): search-oriented input wrapper\n- [calendar](./components/calendar.md): embedded calendar date selector\n- [week-calendar](./components/week-calendar.md): compact week-style date picker\n\n## Navigation And Selection Components\n\n- [tabbar](./components/tabbar.md): bottom-level application navigation family\n- [tabs](./components/tabs.md): page-level tab switching family\n- [navbar](./components/navbar.md): top navigation bar\n- [subsection](./components/subsection.md): compact segmented control family\n- [switch-tab](./components/switch-tab.md): integrated small tab-and-content\n  switcher\n- [index-list](./components/index-list.md): indexed grouped-list navigation\n- [sticky](./components/sticky.md): sticky wrapper for top-pinned content\n- [swiper](./components/swiper.md): carousel / swiper container\n- [scroll-list](./components/scroll-list.md): horizontal scroll-list wrapper\n- [steps](./components/steps.md): workflow step progress family\n- [collapse](./components/collapse.md): collapsible content family\n\n## Data Display And Status Components\n\n- [list](./components/list.md): list-item style cell and content row display\n- [avatar](./components/avatar.md): avatar and avatar-group identity display\n- [badge](./components/badge.md): compact count or status marker\n- [tag](./components/tag.md): lightweight semantic label\n- [title](./components/title.md): section title display\n- [empty](./components/empty.md): empty-state display\n- [footer](./components/footer.md): page footer display\n- [icon](./components/icon.md): icon renderer and icon-name entry point\n- [notice-bar](./components/notice-bar.md): scrolling or inline notice strip\n- [photo-album](./components/photo-album.md): tiled image gallery block\n- [read-more](./components/read-more.md): expandable text/content wrapper\n- [line-progress](./components/line-progress.md): horizontal progress bar\n- [circle-progress](./components/circle-progress.md): circular progress ring\n- [count-down](./components/count-down.md): countdown timer display\n- [count-scroll](./components/count-scroll.md): rolling digit number display\n- [count-to](./components/count-to.md): animated number interpolation\n- [loading](./components/loading.md): animated loading indicator\n- [loadmore](./components/loadmore.md): list-tail loading state component\n\n## Layout And Utility-Oriented Components\n\n- [lazy-load](./components/lazy-load.md): deferred image/content loading\n- [water-fall](./components/water-fall.md): masonry-style multi-column layout\n\n## Cross-Cutting Family Clues\n\n- For grouped selection patterns, compare\n  [checkbox](./components/checkbox.md),\n  [radio](./components/radio.md),\n  [tabs](./components/tabs.md),\n  [tabbar](./components/tabbar.md), and\n  [subsection](./components/subsection.md)\n- For popup-style interaction, compare\n  [popup](./components/popup.md),\n  [modal](./components/modal.md),\n  [action-sheet](./components/action-sheet.md),\n  [notify](./components/notify.md), and\n  [overlay](./components/overlay.md)\n- For list-heavy pages, compare\n  [list](./components/list.md),\n  [scroll-list](./components/scroll-list.md),\n  [swipe-action](./components/swipe-action.md),\n  [loadmore](./components/loadmore.md),\n  [sticky](./components/sticky.md), and\n  [index-list](./components/index-list.md)\n- For temporal input, compare\n  [picker](./components/picker.md),\n  [date-time-picker](./components/date-time-picker.md),\n  [calendar](./components/calendar.md), and\n  [week-calendar](./components/week-calendar.md)\n\n## Coverage Notes\n\n- All current public top-level TNUI components in this repo have linked docs\n- `tag` is documented but currently has no dedicated demo page in the repo\n- `base/` remains an internal shared layer and is not documented as a\n  standalone component\n- Coverage details and exceptions are tracked in\n  [components/README.md](./components/README.md)\n";
